{"tid":545082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港共霸權] 泛民踩場被阻 東區區議會流會告終","createTime":"2018-01-30T07:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T07:44:28.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c7cc7c834803bd7b1edd56008b66cd5876bad2","tid":545082,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"東區區議會今日召開會議，東區泛民會議10名區議員趁港島區選舉主任鄧如欣列席會議，計劃動議緊急加入議程，要求她解釋取消香港眾志周庭參選資格的權力，周庭、黃之鋒等亦以公眾人士列席會議。<br />\n<br />\n不過，會議開始前，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有數名人士阻撓包括東區泛民會議10名區議員等多名區議員進入會議室</strong></span>，場面混亂，區議會15分鐘後因爲不夠會議法定人數而流會"},{"pid":"747513cbbf03ef0f50565751a29fb49e10bd8f73","tid":545082,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"立法會議員被阻開會係犯法，唔知區議會係咪一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8167ee2f8be8c6e68beadf1296e45d00cf1a1fc","tid":545082,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"區議會有權利的嗎? <br />\n唔係每年任務係賤種建制派派錢比佢地班衛星吸血組織買票咩"},{"pid":"93cdd7f571e31e8c3b78882a0e19c0556d69c0ae","tid":545082,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"比起真實型槍game(如戰地風雲，cod 同rainbow 6等等)，我反而更鍾意玩奇幻型（borderlands同bioshock，主角有得用魔法或超能力），呢種槍game會愈玩愈爽！"},{"pid":"acc4f0d802763185f78de0dbb343d6a35c849c95","tid":545082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img